@node VOLRA "Volrath's Stronghold"

@{b}Volrath's Stronghold@{ub}


Color   = Land
Rarity  = Rare
Type    = Legendary  Land
Artist  = Kev Walker

Text(SH): <T>: Add one colorless mana to your mana pool.
           1B, T: Put target creature card from your graveyard on top of
           your library.

Flavor Text: @{i}The seed of a world's evil.@{ui}

